plot: When Nick (David Giuntoli) and Hank (Russell Hornsby) investigate a drowning death with mysterious marks on the victim's ankles, they happen upon a group of water-bound Wesen. Meanwhile, Rosalee (Bree Turner) starts unpacking her things at Monroe's (Silas Weir Mitchell), and Captain Renard (Sasha Roiz) makes a startling realization about the possible identities of the Royal Baby's parents.—Anonymous

When two young lover couples go swimming in a lake, Jake Barnes barely survives an attempt to save his buddy Dominic while their girls shy away, but one's kid sister, who has the hots for Jack, saves him from the naiad, an evil mermaid. While Nick's team, tracing claw-marks, deals with the surviving Mahario family and the naiad code of silence, Renard and his Vienna agent worry about claims to the royal throne and Adalind's possible key part.—KGF Vissers
